    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014definitely ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, utilizing VarioCam Plus for a broad torque curve and 320 hp. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed G96 manual transmission. This example features a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced clutch assembly, ensuring mechanical longevity. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the factory geometry while improving high-speed stability. The hydraulic steering rack provides exceptional tactile feedback, a hallmark of this era. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is sharp. A mechanically sorted driver's car perfect for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Reliable engine. Clean interior. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
