      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s clean, comfortable, and just waiting for its next adventure. Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
