    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and atmospheric induction via six individual throttle bodies. This example utilizes the traditional 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The mechanical assembly is robust, featuring a documented double VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis is enhanced with a refreshed cooling system and Bilstein dampers, providing the precise damping rates required for spirited lateral transitions. While the interior and paint exhibit a light patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain remains in excellent health with linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
